                        <head>334. Editorial Note</head>
                        <p>On July 11, <persName corresp="#p_HHF1">Holland</persName> forwarded a
                            memorandum to <persName corresp="#p_DAW1">Dulles</persName> entitled,
                            “Importance of Present United States Relations with Argentina, Brazil
                            and Chile.” The memorandum is printed as <ref target="#d214">Document
                                214</ref>.</p>
